Page[64]=new Array("If the InForm application uses automated deployments, you must follow these steps to append the InForm Users group to the security descriptor of the InForm Publisher service:","Log in to the InForm application server as an administrator and open a command prompt window.","Get the SID for the InForm Users group by running the following command:","wmic group where (name=&quot;InForm Users&quot;) get sid","The command returns an SID with the following format:","SID","S-x-x-xx-xxxxxxxxx-xxxxxxxx-xxxxxxxxx-xxxx","where S-x-x-xx-xxxxxxxxx-xxxxxxxx-xxxxxxxxx-xxxx is the SID of the InForm Users group.","Get the current security descriptor for the InForm Publisher service by running the following command:","sc sdshow &quot;InForm Publisher Service&quot;","The command returns a security descriptor similar to the following:","D:(A;;CCLCSWRPWPDTLOCRRC;;;SY)(A;;CCDCLCSWRPWPDTLOCRSDRCWDWO;;;BA)(A;;CCLCSWLOCRRC;;;IU)(A;;CCLCSWLOCRRC;;;SU)","Add the SID returned in step 2 to the descriptor returned in step 3 by running the following command:","sc sdset &quot;InForm Publisher Service&quot; D:(A;;CCLCSWRPWPDTLOCRRC;;;SY)(A;;CCDCLCSWRPWPDTLOCRSDRCWDWO;;;BA)(A;;CCLCSWLOCRRC;;;IU)(A;;CCLCSWLOCRRC;;;SU)(A;;RPWPDTLO;;;S-x-x-xx-xxxxxxxxx-xxxxxxxx-xxxxxxxxx-xxxx)","Updating the InForm Publisher service security descriptor—for automated deployments only","220847.htm");
